          <div class="reviewer-avatar">RS</div>
          <div class="reviewer-name">
            Rahul S.
            <span>Verified Customer</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-stars" style="color: #f59e0b;">★★★★★</div>
      </div>
      <p class="review-text">"Very prompt and professional service. The technician arrived right on schedule, quickly identified the issue with my AC not cooling, and resolved it in no time. Will definitely book again."</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Review 2 -->
    <div class="review-card">
      <div class="review-header">
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar">AV</div>
          <div class="reviewer-name">
            Amit V.
            <span>Verified Customer</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-stars" style="color: #f59e0b;">★★★★★</div>
      </div>
      <p class="review-text">"Excellent experience booking a service through this platform. The pricing was completely transparent with no hidden charges. The cooling works perfectly now."</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Review 3 -->
    <div class="review-card">
      <div class="review-header">
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar">MT</div>
          <div class="reviewer-name">
            Mohd T.
            <span>Verified Customer</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="review-stars" style="color: #f59e0b;">★★★★☆</div>
      </div>
      <p class="review-text">"Very satisfied with the AC cleaning service. The team did a neat and clean job, and cleaned up after themselves. Great value for money and very polite behavior."</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding: 40px 24px; background-color: var(--bg-card); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin-bottom: 60px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 30px;">
  <div>
    <h4 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;">Trust & Reliability</h4>
    <h3 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--text-main);">Why Homeowners Choose Aman AC Service</h3>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Our team provides robust guarantees, safe technicians, and modern appointment tracking systems to ensure complete peace of mind.</p>
  </div>
  <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;">
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start;">
      <span style="font-size: 20px; background-color: var(--success-light); color: var(--success); padding: 8px; border-radius: 50%; line-height: 1; display: inline-flex;">✔</span>
      <div>
        <h5 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 2px;">Fully Certified Techs</h5>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted);">All team members hold certified HVAC diagnostics clearances.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start;">
      <span style="font-size: 20px; background-color: var(--success-light); color: var(--success); padding: 8px; border-radius: 50%; line-height: 1; display: inline-flex;">✔</span>
      <div>
        <h5 style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 2px;">Genuine Replacements</h5>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted);">We use brand-verified equipment for sustainable fixes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
